% Public API
- `normalize_simplify_engine(engine: Optional[str], *, default: str = "claude") -> str`
- `resolve_simplify_engine(engine: str) -> str`
- `check_simplify_engine_available(engine: str, *, quiet: bool) -> Tuple[str, str, Optional[str]]`
- `run_simplify_engine_command(engine: str, rel_files: Sequence[str], repo_root: Path, *, focus: str, verbose: bool, quiet: bool, timeout: float) -> Tuple[bool, str, float, str]`

